                                    <lb/>son a þessa Bok <lb/> m<expan>ed</expan> riettv <lb/>
                                       en<expan>n</expan> eingin<expan>n</expan> <lb/>
                                       an<expan>n</expan>ar <lb/> an<expan>n</expan>o 1645</q>
                                 [1695?] og <q>Þördur Iönsson ä Sogu þessa <lb/> A1696</q>.</item>
                              <item n="2">Athugasemd eiganda á bl. 59v-60r.</item>
                           </list>
                        </p>
